  <chunk id="aab412e1a2fee75cf3e3fbc911d985ac004f866e.c4" text="Our study provides new insights into virus-induced autophagy and LGG suppression of uncontrolled autophagy and intestinal injury. A better understanding of the antiviral activity of LGG will lead to novel therapeutic strategies for infant infectious diseases.">
